'''Rangi''' were creatures, possibly [[Sentience/Legends|non-sentient]] or semi-sentient, that lived on [[Barab I/Legends|Barab I]]. According to a remark by [[Saba Sebatyne]], it is believed that they were hunted by the [[Barabel/Legends|Barabels]], yet hunted the Barabels in turn. They lived in giant mounds.

==Appearances==
